## Decisions and Action Items

* **Action Item:** **Brian Trammell** to submit [draft-ietf-scone-protocol](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-scone-protocol/) to the AD/IESG for publication.
* **Action Item:** **Mirja Kühlewind** to submit a PR reframing [draft-ietf-scone-applicability-manageability](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-scone-applicability-manageability/) to focus more exclusively on operator manageability advice.
* **Decision:** The working group will not couple the progression of the protocol and manageability drafts; the protocol draft will proceed immediately.
* **Action Item:** Working group participants must submit any new PRs or major comments on [draft-ietf-scone-applicability-manageability](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-scone-applicability-manageability/) by **August 12**.

